     </div>
     <div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA04d256n2-ptr" id="PJA04d256n2">2</a>
      
   <p>Have recovered strength and health (<span class="ref-st" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ &lt;i&gt;The Oxford English Dictionary&lt;/i&gt;, Oxford, 1933; 12 vols. and supplement. ]"><span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">OED</span></span>).</p>

